beer.beer_description: Beneath a haze of tropical intensity, a quiet storm brews. This “white” stout flips expectations with Manilita hops and Blue Dream terpenes, a biscuity malt base, and creamy vanilla. Full and fruity with a milkshake-like mouthfeel, roasted notes linger beneath, delivering a smooth, electrifying balance of contrast and flavour.
